            "title": "松景科技折讓逾9%配股",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">松景科技(01079)宣布以0.3元配股，配股價較上日收市價0.330港元折讓約9.09%。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"松景科技2023年度年報封面\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/09/01079-2023.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"松景科技2023年度年報封面\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/09/01079-2023.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">松景科技2023年度年報封面</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">配售股份數量最多1億股新股，相當全部已發行股約7.54%，及經配售事項擴大後股本約7.01%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">配售事項所得款項淨額約為2941萬元，將用作集團一般營運資金。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15481679-%e6%9d%be%e6%99%af%e7%a7%91%e6%8a%80%e6%8a%98%e8%ae%93%e9%80%be9%e9%85%8d%e8%82%a1",
