            "title": "油價升約1%　連升兩日",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">原油期貨價格升近1%或以上，連升兩日，俄烏談判陷僵局。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"AP圖片\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/03/20250325_GL_source-AP_oil.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"AP圖片\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/03/20250325_GL_source-AP_oil.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">AP圖片</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">倫敦布蘭特期油收報每桶63.26美元，上升59美仙，升幅0.94%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">紐約期油收報每桶59.67美元，上升72美仙，升幅1.22%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">投資者憧憬聯儲局下周減息，而俄烏和平協議談判陷入僵局，削弱市場對恢復俄羅斯石油出口的預期。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15481584-%e6%b2%b9%e5%83%b9%e5%8d%87%e7%b4%841%e3%80%80%e9%80%a3%e5%8d%87%e5%85%a9%e6%97%a5",
