            "title": "中國海外上月合約銷售按年跌26% 今年累計亦跌21.8%",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">中國海外(00688)公布，今年11月合約物業銷售達222.35億元(人民幣．下同)，按年跌26%；涉及樓面77.44萬平方米，按年亦跌29.8%。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：中國海外官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/07/20230720_FI_source-web_00688.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：中國海外官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/07/20230720_FI_source-web_00688.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">圖片來源：中國海外官網</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">今年以來累計合約銷售為2113.99億元，較去年同期減少21.8%；涉及樓面922.84萬平方米，按年下降9.4%。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">截至11月底，中國海外系列公司尚錄得已認購物業銷售約50.68億元，預期將於往後數月內轉化為合約物業銷售。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15480506-%e4%b8%ad%e5%9c%8b%e6%b5%b7%e5%a4%96%e4%b8%8a%e6%9c%88%e5%90%88%e7%b4%84%e9%8a%b7%e5%94%ae%e6%8c%89%e5%b9%b4%e8%b7%8c26-%e4%bb%8a%e5%b9%b4%e7%b4%af%e8%a8%88%e4%ba%a6%e8%b7%8c21-8",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/02/00688-Web.jpg.webp",
            "pub_date": "2025-12-04 17:25:33",
            "source": "bastillepost",
            "kind": 2,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "中海宏洋上月合約銷售按年降43.7% 今年累計跌16.6%",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">中國海外宏洋(00081)公布，今年11月實現合約銷售22.89億元(人民幣．下同)，按年減少43.7%；涉及樓面21.05萬平方米，亦減少38%。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：中國海外宏洋官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/05/20230823_FI_source-web_00081.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：中國海外宏洋官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/05/20230823_FI_source-web_00081.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">圖片來源：中國海外宏洋官網</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">今年以來累計實現合約銷售，則達296.15億元，按年只減少16.6%；涉及樓面267.05萬平方米，按年減少13.8%。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">截至11月底，該公司尚有累計認購未簽約額4.95億元，涉及樓面4.19萬平方米。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15480482-%e4%b8%ad%e6%b5%b7%e5%ae%8f%e6%b4%8b%e4%b8%8a%e6%9c%88%e5%90%88%e7%b4%84%e9%8a%b7%e5%94%ae%e6%8c%89%e5%b9%b4%e9%99%8d43-7-%e4%bb%8a%e5%b9%b4%e7%b4%af%e8%a8%88%e8%b7%8c16-6",
